These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: colombian, mexican
Cigar: cain, fonseca
Birthday: august, april
1. Cigar:cain is on the right of Birthday:august##1
2. Nationality:mexican is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Nationality   | mexican    | colombian |
| Cigar         | fonseca | cain    |
| Birthday     | august     | april      |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: mirinda, sprite
Sport: badminton, water-polo
Birthday: september, march
1. Birthday:march is on the left of Beverage:mirinda##1
2. Sport:badminton is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Beverage      | sprite  | mirinda   |
| Sport   | water-polo | badminton  |
| Birthday     | march   | september |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
