.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
Birthday: october, january
Job: accountant, dancer
Game: poker, go
1. Game:go is on the left of Job:accountant##1
2. Game:poker is on the left or right of Game:go##3
3. Birthday:october is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Birthday    | january | october     |
| Job     | dancer | accountant |
| Game   | go | poker    |

